CES_Freetext_Negative: While the E-Alert search is okay it's not Fantastic. It very limiting having to choose either City or Map etc for a search. I have long been a critic of Matrix through the years, but it's definitely for power users if you need to do more complicated search. I would like to be able to choose one or several cities and then go into the map and defined the area within those cities or city. I would also like to be able to use the map and exclude cities. It would also be great to have a pick list for cities instead of having to input the manually one by one. Probably the best way to do that is to be able to choose a county and then have it only show the cities for that county.
